name: Broad Street Presbyterian Church
directions: You have to go in the side door. If you're looking at the church from Broad Street, the side entrance is on the right side. Once you go in that entrance, you'll go through a double set of doors. Keep going straight. The restroom is clearly marked as a restroom and will be on the right. It's a single person unisex restroom.
comment: This is a church's food pantry but don't worry, there won't be any religious pressure or even religious topics being discussed. You will only be able to use this restroom during food pantry hours which is every weekday from 8:30am to noon. Closed on holidays. There won't be any problems even if you are only there to use the restroom.
